00:19:50,772 --> 00:19:53,567
<c.bg_transparent>Mohon maaf atas kekacauan ini, Pak.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:53,942 --> 00:19:57,070
<c.bg_transparent>- Kami diserang oleh musuh.</c.bg_transparent>
