264
00:20:03,368 --> 00:20:05,537
<c.bg_transparent>Monster?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Apa maksudmu?</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:20:06,663 --> 00:20:08,624
<c.bg_transparent>Kami bunuh tapi tidak mati, Pak</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:20:11,335 --> 00:20:12,878
<c.bg_transparent>Begitu, ya.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:18,050
<c.bg_transparent>Aku menduga itu senjata biologis</c.bg_transparent>
