268
00:20:18,634 --> 00:20:20,260
<c.bg_transparent>tapi Elric bersaudara...</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:20:21,637 --> 00:20:25,807
<c.bg_transparent>Kebetulan kami dibantu oleh</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Fullmetal Alchemist </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>dan adiknya.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:20:26,725 --> 00:20:29,811
<c.bg_transparent>Nampaknya mereka mengetahui sesuatu</c.bg_transparent>
