271
00:20:30,479 --> 00:20:31,813
<c.bg_transparent>tetapi mereka bungkam.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:20:32,648 --> 00:20:38,028
<c.bg_transparent>Akan jadi bencana jika </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>State Alchemist</i></c.bg_transparent>
