273
00:20:38,403 --> 00:20:40,322
<c.bg_transparent>karena itu aku mengurung mereka.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:20:40,489 --> 00:20:42,199
<c.bg_transparent>Kau ingin bertemu mereka?</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:20:43,450 --> 00:20:44,534
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tentu.</i></c.bg_transparent>

276
00:20:45,494 --> 00:20:48,330
<c.bg_transparent><i>- Kau bilang mereka bungkam?</i></c.bg_transparent>
