284
00:21:22,155 --> 00:21:24,408
<c.bg_transparent>sangat peduli terhadap anak-anak, ya?</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:21:25,450 --> 00:21:30,247
<c.bg_transparent>Tak akan aneh wanita seusiaku</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>memiliki satu atau dua anak,</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:21:30,580 --> 00:21:33,000
<c.bg_transparent>tapi saat ini</c.bg_transparent>
