287
00:21:33,458 --> 00:21:34,626
<c.bg_transparent><i>Bicara apa kau ini?</i></c.bg_transparent>

288
00:21:34,751 --> 00:21:38,005
<c.bg_transparent><i>- Pasti banyak pria yang mencarimu.</i></c.bg_transparent>
