291
00:21:52,227 --> 00:21:53,729
<c.bg_transparent>Tubuh yang abadi.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:21:54,229 --> 00:21:56,273
<c.bg_transparent>Rasanya seperti mimpi, bukan?</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:21:59,234 --> 00:22:03,905
<c.bg_transparent>Bagaimana jika kukatakan kepadamu,</c.bg_transparent>
