294
00:22:12,039 --> 00:22:13,540
<c.bg_transparent>Katakan, Jenderal...</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:22:14,666 --> 00:22:18,587
<c.bg_transparent>Apakah kau tertarik</c.bg_transparent>
